"{\"uid\": \"eonline.com-news-1405706-2024-olympics-swimmer-tamara-potocka-collapses-after-womens-200-meter-individual-medley-race\", \"text\": \"Tamara Potocka, a swimmer from Slovakia competing in the 2024 Paris Olympics, received medical assistance moments after completing the Women's 200-Meter individual medley race.  Tamara Potockais receiving medical attention after collapsing poolside at the2024 Olympics.  Moments after completing the Women's 200-Meter individual medley race, the 21-year-old swimmer from Slovakia collapsed as she got out of the water.  Potocka was immediately surrounded by a group of medical attendants, given first aid and carried off on a stretcher, according to theAssociated Press.  Per the publication, she was immediately surrounded by a group of medical attendants, given first aid and carried off on a stretcher.  According to a rep from the Slovak Olympic Team in Paris, the incident was due to an asthma attack.  \\\"Tamara Potocka is an asthmatic,\\\" they shared in an Aug. 2 statement to E! News. \\\"In the medical room she received an oxygen therapy and during this procedure she communicated. Now she will be monitored by doctors in hospital for some time.\\\"  The incident itself unfolded during a live broadcast, leaving spectators, commentators and officials stunned, according to theDaily Mail.  \\\"Fifteen thousand people are now watching an athlete surrounded by medical staff,\\\" one commentator shared per the publication, \\\"and I can assure you it's absolutely silent in here. They have got a stretcher out, they have got an oxygen mask on the athlete, and I am going to say...this looks very serious.\\\"  He added, \\\"We hope that there is nothing more than that.\\\"  Potocka finished seventh in her heat in a time of 2 minutes, 14.20 seconds, per theAP. Her placement does not quality her to advance her to the semifinals of the event.  Your source for entertainment news, celebrities, celeb news, and \\u200bcelebrity gossip. Check o